.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c58a4d1eac0bee8ddb2b4903c4cfef736e51df","tid":1854802,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9408bda7202bf47aa1f7a8279be95711ddeb23f3","tid":1854802,"uid":103230,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.looop.hk/articles/cover/20191004/5c60ae56863db9099f3129672eac50cc.jpg!s728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.looop.hk%2Farticles%2Fcover%2F20191004%2F5c60ae56863db9099f3129672eac50cc.jpg%21s728&h=162e32d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文明倒退到晚清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"其實從來無西化過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c291df61f7a159826b54fad45fd92cf29d696b2d","tid":1854802,"uid":347326,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"雙黃連口服液由金銀花、黃芩、連翹三味中藥組成。中醫認為，這三味中藥具有清熱解毒、表裡雙清的作用。現代醫學研究認為，雙黃連口服液具有廣譜抗病毒、抑菌、提高機體免疫功能的作用，是目前有效的廣譜抗病毒藥物之一。<br />\n<br />\n上海藥物所長期從事抗病毒藥物研究，2003年&ldquo;非典&rdquo;期間，<strong>上海藥物所左建平團隊率先證實雙黃連口服液具有抗SARS冠狀病毒作用,十餘年來又陸續證實雙黃連口服液對流感病毒（H7N9、H1N1、H5N1）、嚴重急性呼吸綜合徵冠狀病毒、中東呼吸綜合徵冠狀病毒具有明顯的抗病毒效應。</strong><br />\n<br />\nFrom 人民日報<br />\n原來屈機成咁，西方醫學係真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f16141cbaa822db14531d25ee7810877162c5b","tid":1854802,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd3897811b27b2e13e3bc256f3b8d0c44daae10f","tid":1854802,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"緊急⚠️⚠️冇人知今日醫護有野搞！！<br />\n幫我入去十連！！<br />\n<br />\n「全城集氣撐醫護！！」今日三個行程終極懶人包！我要所有人出嚟集氣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"韓國黑警強行腰斬 撐香港