tid":1854802,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c291df61f7a159826b54fad45fd92cf29d696b2d","tid":1854802,"uid":347326,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"雙黃連口服液由金銀花、黃芩、連翹三味中藥組成。中醫認為，這三味中藥具有清熱解毒、表裡雙清的作用。現代醫學研究認為，雙黃連口服液具有廣譜抗病毒、抑菌、提高機體免疫功能的作用，是目前有效的廣譜抗病毒藥物之一。<br />\n<br />\n上海藥物所長期從事抗病毒藥物研究，2003年&ldquo;非典&rdquo;期間，<strong>上海藥物所左建平團隊率先證實雙黃連口服液具有抗SARS冠狀病毒作用,十餘年來又陸續證實雙黃連口服液對流感病毒（H7N9、H1N1、H5N1）、嚴重急性呼吸綜合徵冠狀病毒、中東呼吸綜合徵冠狀病毒具有明顯的抗病毒效應。</strong><br />\n<br />\nFrom 人民日報<br />\n原來屈機成咁，西方醫學係真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"廣譜抗病毒<br />\n諾貝爾都攞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a307577c3b8f36ad4c228728b32868cc8edbf9b","tid":1854802,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"咁撚似唐伯虎點秋香入面含笑半步釘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9125fbdfb7e5a7de4ba3ca49f51a276e932c5ee","tid":1854802,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c63e530d24551624bb8cd596b6aa317dc78631b1","tid":1854802,"uid":73092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"484b1a8b5839d68772194891d2cea8d1dbcab1fd","tid":1854802,"uid":199957,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"習近平係神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T9gAJBm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT9gAJBm.jpg&h=92eb5db3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28fe2e38d021147d5fcfced1635c541439e14690","tid":1854802,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:23:14.000Z","msg":"中藥有耐藥性？<br />\n你搞笑咋？"},{"pid":"7116b67c5b3bae7e74b0474ef74be5de225a3218","ti