有效的廣譜抗病毒藥物之一。<br />\n<br />\n上海藥物所長期從事抗病毒藥物研究，2003年&ldquo;非典&rdquo;期間，<strong>上海藥物所左建平團隊率先證實雙黃連口服液具有抗SARS冠狀病毒作用,十餘年來又陸續證實雙黃連口服液對流感病毒（H7N9、H1N1、H5N1）、嚴重急性呼吸綜合徵冠狀病毒、中東呼吸綜合徵冠狀病毒具有明顯的抗病毒效應。</strong><br />\n<br />\nFrom 人民日報<br />\n原來屈機成咁，西方醫學係真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"佢唔好話cancer都醫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344682799a673d2700c8e153cefb849e00e6d67c","tid":1854802,"uid":14653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:48:25.000Z","msg":"掩耳盜鈴咪呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無人信架啦，留返啲打維穩文嘅氣力抗疫好過啦"},{"pid":"b3f2923bead76df515e118dbf15267e9dff49906","tid":1854802,"uid":62950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bhUbgF7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbhUbgF7.jpg&h=d126cb6a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢張圖好過癮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單得黎又夠串班無腦既ON9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b233604beee27ccee14da1127d0e8dafd5e82a82","tid":1854802,"uid":90697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d8c90952e92d2ef4142fa1139a335bc995784c","tid":1854802,"uid":172349,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4OZ906.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4OZ906.jpg&h=f12bccc7&s